This repository is for teaching the basics of how to process iso8583 transactions using erlang .
It contains code for doing just that .
Check it out and tell me what u think !!
Right now i have added erlang code for parsing messages sent using iso8583 ascii format 
But later i intend to add code for parsing both xml,binary and other customer formats .
check it out and give me your comments !!.
